

**Matsh ha doag g Jesus mihshmda tash ed **

*An g neid g Matthew 12:9-14; Luke 6:6-11 *

1 Sh am hu hebai, tsh am ep i wahp idam Jesus hema cheopi ch ed. Kush am hema daha g oꞌodham mash g nowij mahnikodag. 2 Kush am haꞌi dadha g Palasi ch am s‑nenꞌeid mas hab wo juh g doajida am ha mihshmda tash ed nash pi ab haꞌichu s‑abchudamk. 

3 Sh g Jesus hab kaij heg wui mahnikokam, “Ia g hu i kekiwua.” Kutsh gam hu i kekiwua. 

4 Sh ab hahawa ha kakke, “Shahchu am ahgch hab elid mo pi hiwgidas mihshmda tash ed mamt wo i ha wehmt hegam mo e shoꞌigchud? Ab o em‑ab mamt wo i ha wehmt g shoꞌigkam k am wo i e nako mamt wo ha doꞌibia hegam mat am hu wo e koꞌij. Aha namt wabsh wo ha hiwigi mat wo e koꞌij?” 

Kush pi hedai has shaꞌi kaij 5 nash pi pi shaꞌi pihk e elid heg wui mahnikokam. Sh heg hekaj si s‑koꞌokam an i ha nenashad g Jesus ch eda ep pi ap e tahtk ha wehhejed ch ash hab kaij heg wui oꞌodham, “Ab g si i shelin g e‑nowi.” Kutsh am wabsh i chum shelin k am waꞌi hekaj apꞌet. 

6 Kutsh babgat g Palasi matsh ha doaj ha mihshmda tash ab k gam hu hihim k am ha wehm e nam g piongaj hegai mo wa d kownal heg eda chekshani ch hab chehgig Herod. Kush idam e wehm aꞌaga matsh has hig masma wo mua g Jesus. 

**Matsh muꞌi hemajkam am e hemapai ge shuhdagi hugid an **

7 Kutsh gam hu hahawa hihi hegam Jesus ge shuhdagi wui. Kutsh muꞌi hemajkam am i oi ab Galilee t amjed 8 ch ab Judea t amjed, chum hems ab Jerusalem kihhim t amjed, ch Idumia chekshani ch gan hu aigojed g Jordan akimel ch gam hujed mash d Tyre ch Sidon kihhim. Idam muꞌi atsh am himto am kaiok mo heꞌes i geꞌe haꞌichu hab wuihim g Jesus. 

9 Kush heg am ha ahgid hegam mo ab si wecho e mashcham matsh g wahlko an wo uꞌukchid am wehhejed natsh pi g hemajkam wabsh wo i si chehmo. 10 Kush wehs am chum s‑ahimk g kokꞌodam ch ab s‑tahtmamk mat wo ha apꞌet natsh pi muꞌijj ha dodaj. 11 Kutsh hekid wo sha nei g Jesus hegam mash g jijawul ha uꞌukch k ab wo i e shoꞌigch wui k wo si hihin k hab wo chei, “Ahpi ap d Jiosh alidag.” 12 Sh g Jesus am si ha chehani mat pi hedai wo shaꞌi ahgi mo hedai wud. 

**Matsh gamai gohk am i ha chuhcha g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 10:1-4; Luke 6:12-16 *

13-14 Tsh am hu hebai, tsh ab i chesh g Jesus kawulk t ab k ab i wai hegam mash ab s‑wohochud. Tsh ab wui i hihi. Kutsh gamai gohk am i ha chuhcha ab ha wui hab kaijch, “Ahpim amt chum hekid wo ni‑wehmajkad. Kunt hebaichuj am wo em‑cheha mamt am hebai wo hihim k wo ha mihshmad. 15 Kumt wo edgidad g gewkdag mamt gam hu hab wo i ha juh g jijawul ab ha amjed hegam mo an ha uꞌukch.” 16 Neh, bash kaij ch am i ha chuhcha hegam gamai gohk. Hema hegam o d Simon. Kutsh heg hab ep chehch Peter mo hab d ahga Hodai. 17 Haꞌi ehp o d James ch John ch d Zebedee aꞌalidag. Kutsh idam hab ep ha chehch g Jesus ‘Tataniki Namkam.’ 18 Haꞌi ehp o d Andrew, Philip, Bartholomew, Matthew, ch Thomas. K hema d hegai mo d James ch d alidaj hegai mo hab chehgig Alphias. K hema hab ep chehgig Simon ch d hema hegam mo tatchua matt ahchim Tutuligo hejel wo himchudad g t‑kownaltalig. K hema d Thaddaus 19 K hema d hegai mat gagda g Jesus k hab chehgig Judas Iscariot. Neh, idam gamai gohk ash d Jesus chuhchai. Kush an oidchug. 

**Mash g Jesus g Jiawul wehm ab aꞌai e cheggia **

*An g neid g Matthew 12:22-32; Luke 11:14-23 *

20 Kutsh am uhpam hih g Jesus mash am kih. Tsh hegam gamai gohk am i oi. Kutsh g hemajkam am ep i e hemapad k shaꞌi si muꞌida. Tsh heg hekaj pi e nako mas ep wo e gegos idam Jesus. 21 Kutsh am i kah g hahajunij k ab i hihim k am chum s‑behimk hab elidch mat sha heb hu wua g e‑chegitoi. 

22 Sh am hai gegok g chehanig ha mashchamdam ch am dada Jerusalem t amjed ch ash hab kaij, “Jijawul ha‑geꞌejig oki an uꞌukch g chegitoidaj ihda.” 

Sh haꞌi ep hab kaij, “Moki g jijawul ha‑geꞌejig ab mahkch g gewkdag. K id hekaj gam hu hab i ha wua g jijawul ab ha amjed hegam mo an ha uꞌukch.” 

23 Tsh oi wa g Jesus ab i ha waid k hab masma am i ha tashogi, “Kus haschu ahgk hig g Jiawul wo i wuhshad g hejel e‑pionag? 24 S‑mahch am mat g oꞌodham wo padch g hejel e‑jewedga mat ab aꞌai wo e cheggia. 25 Kut g e wehm kihkam hab waꞌap wo padch g hejel e‑kihdag mat ab aꞌai wo e cheggia. 26 Pegih, t has hig masma g jijawul pi wo padch g hejel e‑gewkdag mat ab aꞌai wo e cheggia? 

27 “Neh, wohppoꞌid ani g ge Jiawul hegam mo an ha uꞌukch. Kum s‑mahch mat pi hedai wo shaꞌi e nako mas am hu wabsh wo wah hema kih ed mat wo s‑haꞌahamak k am wo ui g enigaj, heg hi wa matp wehpeg wo wulsh. 

28 “Wehs o gam hu hab i junihog g pi ap ha‑chuꞌijig g Jiosh. 29 K wabshaba si geꞌej g em‑chuꞌijig mamtp ab wo has ah g Hekia S‑apꞌekam Gewkdag. T g Jiosh pi hekid gam hu hab wo i juh.” 30 Bash kaij g Jesus no pi hab ge ahg mash g ge Jiawul uꞌukch. Kush eda d Hekia S‑apꞌekam Gewkdag mo an uꞌukch. 

**Mash g jeꞌej ch wepngaj s‑neidamk g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 12:46-50; Luke 8:19-21 *

31-32 Kutsh am hahawa dada g jeꞌej ch wepngaj g Jesus matsh wo nei. Sh wabshaba muꞌijj an wehgaj dadha g Jesus. Sh heg hekaj gam hu wabsh gegok jeg ed ch am chum waid. Kumsh am ahgid, “Nehꞌe, m‑jeꞌe ch m‑wepnag o am gegok jeg ed ch ab m‑waid.” 

33-34 Sh g Jesus an i nenhoghi. Kush muꞌi an wehgaj dadha hegam mo ab kaiham. Kush hab kaij, “Neh, idam mo ab ni‑kaiham o heg wa wepo mo d ni‑wepnag ch ni‑jeꞌe. 35 Hegam mat hab wo junihid g Jiosh tatchui o hab a masma mo d ni‑wepnag ch ni‑jeꞌe.” 

